Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:33.05,SIGN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\c&HADADAD&}The world of Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.05,Note,,0,0,0,,Shinigami literally means a "God of Death".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}A pair of sleeping skulls?!
